# [MPLS](../wg/mpls.html)

## Summary

The MPLS Working Group met during the IETF 120 session. The meeting covered administrative updates, errata processing, and several technical presentations focusing on MPLS Network Actions (MNA) for operations, administration, and maintenance (OAM), telemetry, and deterministic networking (DetNet). Key topics included capability discovery via LSP Ping, ECN over MNA, and RSVP-TE tunneling optimizations on SR-MPLS forwarding planes.

